So, I believe with all my heart, it's a time like never before to send out the greater things in prayer—just praying in the spirit and seeking Him daily.

00:07:57.840 --> 00:08:03.892
So, my wife—I brought her on here today because she's going to read to you a prophetic word that was given.

00:08:03.892 --> 00:08:09.598
And I know some people may have heard this before, but it's worth repeating.

