And so I believe it's good to listen to this again. Someone emailed this to us. Yes, and it blessed me. It blessed my wife.

00:08:32.593 --> 00:08:42.220
We both were like, 'Whoa!'Because there was a lot of things that we saw coming in 2015 that didn't quite manifest the way the prophetic voice is saying.

00:08:42.221 --> 00:08:51.115
And I believe this is why. But I'm telling you, it's the one last call.

