The time is setting on this dispensation of grace, and God is giving us one last call to bring in a harvest of souls.

00:09:00.066 --> 00:09:04.079
And I believe this is where we are. So, if you want to start reading, babe, I'll let you go.

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:08.799
I had a vision, a prophetic experience as I was eating lunch recently.

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:15.877
Suddenly, a portal opened in the spirit realm, and my angel said to me, "You are summoned to come to the courtroom of heaven.

00:09:15.878 --> 00:09:23.072
You are to record the case being tried now so that God's people will know the lateness of the hour.

00:09:23.073 --> 00:09:29.805
You must warn them so that the bride may awaken and take heed. The time is short."Thank you, Father.

00:09:29.806 --> 00:09:35.564
I was escorted by two angels to a seat on the left side down front of the Supreme Courtroom.

00:09:35.565 --> 00:09:39.980
There were many hundreds of angels and saints already seated before the bench.

00:09:39.981 --> 00:09:47.354
I was surprised how much it looked like our Supreme Court room in America, except it was much larger.

00:09:47.355 --> 00:09:54.159
It looked more like a giant arena with thousands of seats ascending up as far as I could see.

00:09:54.160 --> 00:10:00.256
There were five big leather warrior-like chairs with wings on each side in the front row.

00:10:00.257 --> 00:10:09.393
They reminded me very much of the kind of chairs my father always sat in behind his desk at his law firm years ago.

00:10:09.394 --> 00:10:16.858
There were gold embossed cards on them that said 'recorder'on all five of these chairs.

00:10:16.859 --> 00:10:22.994
I must have been the first to arrive, and I was ushered into the one closest to the bench.

00:10:22.995 --> 00:10:30.479
I sat down and sunk into this really comfortable chair and was handed a pen and a small scroll.

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:34.714
I was curious as I looked at it, for it looked really old-fashioned.

00:10:34.715 --> 00:10:42.998
The pen was a feather quill with an old-fashioned nib like a fountain pen at the bottom to write with.

00:10:42.999 --> 00:10:52.015
The pad was a scroll that was made out of parchment. It would open automatically as you wrote upon it when you got to the bottom of the page.

00:10:52.016 --> 00:10:58.255
It was kind of like an iPad that looked like a small Torah scroll at the same time.

00:10:58.256 --> 00:11:04.065
The angel showed me how it worked. It was extremely easy to hold and write on.

00:11:04.066 --> 00:11:11.763
When I would start to write, it would write whatever I thought of in perfect calligraphy script as fast as I thought it.

00:11:11.764 --> 00:11:16.168
The nib seemed to just fly over the parchment with ease in my hand.

00:11:16.169 --> 00:11:28.776
It would write whatever the angel put in my mind from what I saw and heard to record, and then it would describe perfectly any other information the Holy Spirit deemed important in an instant as it happened.

00:11:28.777 --> 00:11:35.838
It was the easiest thing I have ever written. It seemed to do all the work without my thinking or trying.

00:11:35.839 --> 00:11:40.392
I think this must have been heaven's way of court legal stenography.

00:11:40.393 --> 00:11:46.396
Most amazing of all, I was writing in Hebrew, and I hardly know the language at all.

00:11:46.397 --> 00:11:54.233
But somehow I understood and thought in fluent Hebrew during this vision. I cannot offer any explanation for this at all.

00:11:54.234 --> 00:12:02.038
The angel said, "You are one of five prophet recorders that have been summoned from the earth to chronicle and witness this trial soon to begin.

00:12:02.039 --> 00:12:07.413
Just let the pen flow over the parchment and it will be a witness to the proceedings.

00:12:07.414 --> 00:12:19.999
Then you will sign it when it is finished and it will be added to the eternal ledger of legal proceedings."Soon the other four recorders were seated and shown how to write as I was.

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:26.199
I recognized one of them as a current prophet on earth. He was the only other from the western world.

00:12:26.200 --> 00:12:30.798
I cannot speak of whom it was at this time, and the other three of them were not known to me.

00:12:30.799 --> 00:12:34.140
We were all different races from different regions of the earth.

00:12:34.141 --> 00:12:39.919
One was a Chinese woman of great age who just glowed with the wisdom and love of God.

00:12:39.920 --> 00:12:45.943
We were dressed in black robes with red border sashes on the sides and the sleeves.

00:12:45.944 --> 00:12:55.838
The other prophet recorder was a lady from Africa who had a headdress that wrapped around her head which flashed rays of light whenever she moved.

00:12:55.839 --> 00:13:02.879
She spoke and wrote in French, I believe. The fifth was a man from South America.

00:13:02.880 --> 00:13:09.439
I was given a yarmulke of golden color. It had 12 ruby stones around it.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:16.185
God called me to wear a yarmulke whenever I minister on earth. So I wasn't surprised that I had to wear one here.

00:13:16.186 --> 00:13:25.517
When the angel put it on my head, I could feel the weight of it like it was made out of actual metal gold, even though it felt soft to the touch like silk.

00:13:25.518 --> 00:13:37.131
Everyone finally assembled and a great and beautiful angel who presided over the courtroom named Justice stood up. She seemed to tower over us and was about 20 ft tall.

00:13:37.132 --> 00:13:44.310
Then angels appeared with long trumpets on either side of the courtroom and sounded a fanfare that ended with a blast.

00:13:44.311 --> 00:13:52.798
The angel Justice then shouted with a very loud soprano voice, "All rise.

00:13:52.799 --> 00:14:08.989
The Honorable Ancient of Days, the Judge of All Creation, the King of Ages, the Most High Lord Almighty is present and presiding."We all stood up exactly at the same time in unison.

00:14:08.990 --> 00:14:17.194
Then the most awesome sound of praise and worship filled the atmosphere as we all began to praise his glorious majesty together.

00:14:17.195 --> 00:14:23.600
I have never experienced such a sense of awe as the fear of the Lord filled the court.

00:14:23.601 --> 00:14:32.990
It was only then that I could just make out who was seated behind the holy bar. There were not nine judges but 12.

00:14:32.991 --> 00:14:38.272
God the Father sat in the middle with six of the Supreme Court judges on both sides of him.

00:14:38.273 --> 00:14:43.030
I somehow knew he was the final deciding vote in every decision.

00:14:43.031 --> 00:14:50.845
After our praises finished, the angel Justice, who I now saw was a lady and not a male angel, shouted, "Be seated.

00:14:50.846 --> 00:14:56.638
The high court is now in session."She was standing just in front of his throne.

00:14:56.639 --> 00:15:01.417
She had a golden gavel and struck a giant crystalline base with it.

00:15:01.418 --> 00:15:08.719
There was a great thunder clap and lightning flashed out from the gavel base and flew across the room in all directions.

00:15:08.720 --> 00:15:12.564
It was only then that I could see the judges behind the bench.

00:15:12.565 --> 00:15:22.078
The only person that I could not see the face of was the Father, but I could see the throne he sat upon and the outline of his face.

00:15:22.079 --> 00:15:31.573
He seemed to be clothed in a white blinding light as well. He had a black robe on, but had every color of the rainbow flashing out of it.

00:15:31.574 --> 00:15:38.754
If he moved even slightly, lightning bolts would fly all over the room, out of his head, his hands, and his feet.

00:15:38.755 --> 00:15:52.435
The other judges to the Father's right hand were Enoch, Father Abraham, Moses the lawgiver, David the King, Elijah the prophet, and Daniel.

00:15:52.436 --> 00:16:00.085
On the Father's left hand were John the Baptist, Peter, James, John, Andrew, and Paul the Apostle.

00:16:00.086 --> 00:16:08.877
I do not know whether these were the permanent judges of the Supreme Court of Heaven or not, but those were the ones seated for this case.

00:16:08.878 --> 00:16:15.569
They were all also dressed in these black iridescent judge robes.

00:16:15.570 --> 00:16:22.317
There were stunning crowns of glory on each of their heads and they were holding gold scepters in their right hands.

00:16:22.317 --> 00:16:32.278
The Father in the middle on the throne of judgment held the biggest scepter and had many crowns suspended over his head that shot lightnings out of them in every direction.

00:16:32.279 --> 00:16:39.459
I could not look upon them or his face because it was so bright. It was like looking into the noonday sun.

00:16:39.460 --> 00:16:43.877
I was given one glimpse at him when he first came into the courtroom.

00:16:43.878 --> 00:16:51.452
There was a rainbow that would appear that encircled him above and below that I saw a few times during this vision.

00:16:51.452 --> 00:16:59.960
I could not endure looking at him for more than a split second before I had to avert my eyes, for the white blazing brightness was too intense.

00:16:59.961 --> 00:17:06.118
All the judges behind the great bar were emanating great light that was also nearly blinding.

00:17:06.119 --> 00:17:13.202
That is the closest I can describe them now. Then the case was read before all present by Lady Justice, the angel.

00:17:13.203 --> 00:17:19.230
She spoke: "This is the summary of the case brought before the Supreme Court of Heaven today.

00:17:19.231 --> 00:17:24.636
The timing of the final judgments of the day of the Lord must be decided.

00:17:24.637 --> 00:17:46.479
The accuser, Satan, is prosecuting, declaring that the time of Adam's lease is over, and he must be allowed to take ownership of the earth for a time and times and half a time as it is written in the Holy Scriptures."That is the most amazing, babe.

00:17:46.480 --> 00:17:54.636
Representing the holy defense is the Lord Yeshua, Jesus the Messiah, the Lamb of God.

00:17:54.637 --> 00:18:03.597
At this, Yeshua himself stood up at the defense table as the advocate general of the bride of Messiah on earth.

00:18:03.598 --> 00:18:08.262
He was representing the holy saints of God still alive in their bodies on earth.

00:18:08.263 --> 00:18:15.537
When he stood up at the left table, everyone bowed and worshiped except those at the prosecution table to the right.

00:18:15.538 --> 00:18:22.615
There was a very handsome man who just sat stone-faced with several other princes at the prosecution table.

00:18:22.616 --> 00:18:30.239
They did not move. The headman sneered when they worshiped Yeshua.

00:18:30.240 --> 00:18:37.359
Representing the agenda of the fallen Lucifer, now called Satan, is the accuser, liar, and deceiver himself.

00:18:37.360 --> 00:18:42.003
Satan! At this, the handsome prince with the evil smirk stood up.

00:18:42.004 --> 00:18:46.360
No one moved. There was silence in the courtroom for about a minute.

00:18:46.361 --> 00:18:53.930
Then Lady Justice spoke again, "You may sit down now."Finally, he did so with another sneering grunt.

00:18:53.931 --> 00:19:02.416
I marveled that he seemed human and actually very attractive to look at, although there was no heavenly light in him or around him.

00:19:02.417 --> 00:19:08.073
"The prosecution may proceed,"Lady Justice proclaimed. At this, the man stood up.

00:19:08.074 --> 00:19:14.253
He was robed in a black suit that had a long cape of crimson red that followed behind him.

00:19:14.254 --> 00:19:18.782
He had gold epaulettes on his shoulders that were built into his cape.

00:19:18.783 --> 00:19:24.990
He was very articulate and extremely haughty. I got sick to my stomach as he spoke.

00:19:24.991 --> 00:19:29.889
He walked back and forth in front of the courtroom in long strides with his nose in the air.

00:19:29.890 --> 00:19:35.956
It reminded me of a painting of what Napoleon looked like, except this man was much taller than Napoleon.

00:19:35.957 --> 00:19:44.739
He began his long diatribe of accusation against fallen man. He seemed to know the Bible very well.

00:19:44.740 --> 00:19:49.634
Starting from Adam and Eve, he began accusing God of failing mankind in every generation.

00:19:49.635 --> 00:19:57.735
He started with this stipulation: Adam was given nearly 6,000 years to rule the earth. He gave that lease to me, and I own it.

00:19:57.736 --> 00:20:04.651
I have the right to rule over every man, woman, and child who are mine by Adam's free choice. The time is up.

00:20:04.652 --> 00:20:10.096
I now demand the government of mankind be given to me through whom you call the son of perdition.

00:20:10.097 --> 00:20:15.999
I call him my son of man. I have the scriptural right to take control of the earth for seven years.

00:20:16.000 --> 00:20:22.474
Give it to me now. Then he sat down again for about a minute or so. There was complete silence.

00:20:22.475 --> 00:20:32.788
Lady Justice then spoke again, "The defense may proceed."Yeshua then arose from the defense table.

00:20:32.789 --> 00:20:43.472
He wore a white robe with blue trim and red sleeves with a bottom border and neck border of red. He wore a small diadem of solid diamonds as a crown.

00:20:43.473 --> 00:20:49.858
Once again, when he stood up, everyone bowed their heads before him to worship except those at the prosecution table.

00:20:49.859 --> 00:21:00.763
He said, "In summary, as the true son of man, I have taken the death penalty for every generation of fallen man, including those in this harvest generation.

00:21:00.764 --> 00:21:09.595
I also strip Satan of his authority over the church of the living God. His gates can no longer prevail against her.

00:21:09.596 --> 00:21:27.562
Through the intercession of my holy bride on earth, the overcoming church of the living God, there has been granted a pause in this court to allow for the fullness of the harvest to come in during the last hearing on this matter in 2015, three years ago in earth's time.

00:21:27.563 --> 00:21:36.932
For I spoke on earth as it is written, this gospel of the kingdom shall be preached in all the world and then the end shall come.

00:21:36.933 --> 00:22:21.566
I, by the authority of the prayers and intercession of the bride documented here in this scroll,"he handed the scroll to the Father and another copy of it to Satan's prosecution table, "I petition the court for another measure of time for the end-time church to finish and fulfill the promise to my people, as it is written that none should perish but all who are truly mine have the opportunity to hear the good news of the gospel and to be saved from perdition."As he was speaking, Satan, the handsome man lawyer, was busy reading the scroll feverishly to see if there was truly enough intercession to stop his immediate seizing of the earth and for the tribulation to begin.

00:22:21.567 --> 00:22:33.939
He was consulting his other diabolical lawyers about it. Foul language was coming out of his mouth along with hissing and accusing his right-hand man, saying, "You told me we had destroyed the prayers of the church.

00:22:33.940 --> 00:22:41.678
The great awakening has been thwarted."Then he said curse words.

00:22:41.679 --> 00:22:51.949
Yeshua continued, "As you can see, my faithful bridal remnant has kept the faith, enduring the evil and continuing to overcome.

00:22:51.950 --> 00:22:57.215
The blood of the martyrs has proven their faithfulness. Look at China.

00:22:57.216 --> 00:23:02.604
Look at the Middle East. Look at Africa. Look at Indonesia. Look at South America.

00:23:02.605 --> 00:23:08.177
Look at the islands of the sea. Look at my persecuted bride in all nations.

00:23:08.178 --> 00:23:12.317
Even America has held, though all hell has been thrown against her.

00:23:12.318 --> 00:23:18.046
The facts speak for themselves. I have the authority to request another extension of time.

00:23:18.047 --> 00:23:26.239
The defense petitions the court for another extension of time in the grace that I purchased by my blood on the cross.

00:23:26.240 --> 00:23:38.071
Also, I petition the court to look into the scrolls of the hidden counsels written before the foundations of the earth regarding the mysteries of the harvest of the end of days.

00:23:38.072 --> 00:23:41.942
These Satan has no knowledge of, as they were never shown to him.

00:23:41.943 --> 00:23:56.695
It is written there, as well as in the hidden revelation of scripture, that the tribulation beginning the kingdom age must begin only after all of my bride that I ordained to eternal life are saved and come to the knowledge of truth.

00:23:56.696 --> 00:24:03.246
This information can be found in the scroll given by my hands to the court for eternal record.

00:24:03.247 --> 00:24:08.534
The evidence written in this scroll fully confirms and documents our holy and righteous claim.

00:24:08.535 --> 00:24:18.879
Though millions shall come to me and be saved in the tribulation to come, my holy bride must all be prepared now."Then there came a time of silence.

